Package weka.classifiers.timeseries.core

Interface Summary
ConfidenceIntervalForecaster Interface to a forecaster that can compute confidence intervals for its forecasts
IncrementallyPrimeable An interface to a forecaster that can be primed incrementally.
OverlayForecaster Interface to a forecaster that has been trained with data containing "overlay" attributes.
TSLagUser Interface to something that uses the TSLagMaker class.
 

Class Summary
AbstractTimeSeriesFilter Re-written version of weka.filters.unsupervised.attribute.AbstractTimeSeriesFilter that adds new methods and uses java.utils collection classes.
CustomPeriodicTest Class that evaluates a supplied date against user-specified date constant fields.
ErrorBasedConfidenceIntervalEstimator Class that computes confidence intervals for a time series forecaster using errors computed on the training data.
TimeSeriesTranslate Re-written version of weka.filters.unsupervised.attribute.TimeSeriesTranslate.
TSLagMaker A class for creating lagged versions of target variable(s) for use in time series forecasting.
TSLagMaker.PeriodicityHandler Helper class to manage time stamp manipulation with respect to various periodicities.
Utils Static utility routines.
 

Enum Summary
CustomPeriodicTest.Operator Enum defining inequality operations
TSLagMaker.Periodicity Enum defining periodicity
